title: Scientology Church Locations, World, 12.2007
name: Scientology Church Locations, World, 12.2007
description: This dataset displays the location of Scientology churches worldwide. This data was collected from http://www.churchofscientology.com/, and was geocoded according to address in order to find the latitude and longitude measurements.             On December 3, 2007 an article released by the MSNBC at: http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/22083928/            Speaks about a motion proposed by a German official to ban the Scientology practice in Germany.             The geocoding process was was unable to code for a few of the 130+ churches.
